</li><li> <a href="/Version_2.6" title="Version 2.6">2.6.0</a>&nbsp;: Added the <code>current_category</code> parameter.
</li><li> <a href="/Version_2.7.1" title="Version 2.7.1">2.7.1</a>&nbsp;: Added the <code>exclude_tree</code> parameter.
